# shadcn (marketing)

## Source of truth

- `components.json` — style `base-nova`, aliases `@/components/ui`.
- Add components via shadcn CLI; do not fork primitives for marketing-only styling.

## Usage

- Marketing-specific layout belongs in `src/components/marketing/primitives/`, composing `ui/*` where needed.
- Use `cn()` from `@/lib/utils` for class merging.
- Button brand variants: `variant="brandPrimary"` etc. as defined in project button component.

## Registries

- Additional blocks may come from configured registries in `components.json` — prefer existing marketing primitives before importing heavy external blocks.
